game.name: Military Defense Strike
game.description:
This time we are going to take you to a completely new action-packed challenge where you also have to test your sharp hand-eye coordination abilities! Are you ready friends? Join Military Defense Strike and show off the world that you are skilled enough to aim and fire your enemies! Grab your heavy machine gun and get ready to protect your home base against deadly enemies! The gameplay is simple, but comes with several unexpected challenges when you are involved. 
Your primary objective in this single player shooter game is to defend your position and protect your home base while attacking at the defined targets at the same and right time. The enemies are big in number and keep approaching your base to defeat you. The problem is that their power keeps increasing with each level you progress. So be prepared to face off the stronger enemies in the present level as compared to what you dealt in the previous one. 
All it takes to put your fighting abilities to the test to defeat them in each level and secure the maximum possible points in the end in this html5 shooting game. Use your mouse on desktop and tap the screen on mobile phone to kill bad guys each time! Clicking at the right time on the screen will guide you towards the victory! In case of feeling bored, check out more defense games for boys on atmegame.com. The huge collection of military games will also have a lot to offer to all and you can enjoy them without download.
